Description: UniGent Autonomous AI Agent
 A universal autonomous AI agent powered by NVIDIA NIM API.
 It features streaming responses, persistent memory, file operations, shell commands, web search, parallel tool execution, and more.
 Note: This package requires the 'openai' Python package, which is not available from Debian.
 Install it via pip: pip3 install openai
